Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.24,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,MAAM'S TURMOIL
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.30,0:01:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He's paralyzed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.80,0:02:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you shoot Dai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.83,0:02:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down! Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can move!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.49,0:02:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I can move my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.50,0:02:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.80,0:02:37.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you move?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.76,0:02:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.65,0:02:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,That was Kiari.\NA spell that cures paralysis and numbness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I shot him with Kiariku to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:53.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We were interrupted...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.77,0:02:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but you merely\Nextended your life a few moments!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.67,0:03:03.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit, what is that weapon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.05,0:03:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! Can you cast Hyado?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.24,0:03:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! My Ice-type spells\Nare unparalleled...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.87,0:03:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget the bragging!\NLoad it into this bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.13,0:03:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Press the stone at the top\Nand cast the spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.17,0:03:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.36,0:03:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Hyadaruko!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.85,0:03:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.70,0:03:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,The sun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.58,0:03:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,How's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You dare scar my face...\NNo, my pride!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.63,0:04:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember this, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear I'll kill you! I swear it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.23,0:04:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.66,0:04:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.02,0:04:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, how could you ditch me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.54,0:04:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, that was...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.05,0:04:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So you really did abandon him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my Magic Bullet Gun.\NIt was a gift from Master Avan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You load spells\Ninto the Magic Bullets and fire them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.23,0:04:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. So it's shoots\Nattack and heal spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.94,0:04:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so you're\Na student of Master Avan, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.07,0:04:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That explains your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.48,0:04:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.34,0:04:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Much better.\NYour Midheal is better than Grampa's.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.86,0:04:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, could I get a heal spell, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.10,0:04:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Here! Medicinal herbs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.18,0:04:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell!\NWhat's this difference in treatment?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.33,0:04:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The difference between\Na Hero and a coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.49,0:05:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,These clouds bode ill tidings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope nothing's happened to Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.87,0:05:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this terrible presence?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You must be Brass, the Lump Shaman.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.56,0:05:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Army?! Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This island is protected\Nby Sir Avan's Magic Circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when Hadlar breached it,\Nthere was a huge tremor!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.37,0:05:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,How could anyone come in so easily?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.98,0:05:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With my Mystic Magic Power\Nit's mere child's play.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the Mystic Bishop Zaboera.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Legion Commander of the Mystic Legion,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:58.42,On Top,,0,0,0,,LEGION COMMANDER OF THE MYSTIC LEGION\NMYSTIC BISHOP ZABOERA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.21,0:05:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,one of the Six Legions of the Dark Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Gomechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.55,0:06:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.57,0:06:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course she is!\NMaam's tough like a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I mean, she's like a saint!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.70,0:06:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.94,0:06:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam, who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.87,0:06:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,They're nobody suspicious, Elder.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.78,0:06:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They're Heroes fighting the Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.99,0:06:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,They are?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, Gomechan was\Nthe only one who never went crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So your name's Gomechan!\NI'm glad you were reunited!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe Gomechan has some power\Nthat blocks the Dark Lord's influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just glad we're reunited.\NThank you, Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.13,0:06:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.44,0:06:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to introduce my mother, Leira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:06:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.97,0:07:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, these two are\NMaster Avan's students, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.21,0:07:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sir Avan's?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You know Master Avan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:11.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom and my late father\Nfought the Dark Lord with Master Avan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.89,0:07:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.66,0:07:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,My husband was a Warrior\Nand I was a Priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together, we aided Sir Avan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After the Dark Lord was vanquished\Nand peace was restored,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Avan visited this village once.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.45,0:07:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when he tutored Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That was four or five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.75,0:07:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's already been that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.67,0:07:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So, is Sir Avan well?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.63,0:07:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Uh, er...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.09,0:07:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,He's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.07,0:07:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He's as lively as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dai...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You should stay here a while after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd love to hear about Master Avan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, we wouldn't want to intrude.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.63,0:08:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea. Please, stay a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.78,0:08:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We really shouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.36,0:08:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay! Stay! That way\NI get to play with Gomechan again!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.57,0:08:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna play, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.95,0:08:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.87,0:08:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole village welcomes\Nany student of Sir Avan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of the men\Nhave gone to protect Romos Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.71,0:08:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So the rest of us\Nprotect the village together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,With you in the lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.66,0:08:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,My father was a Warrior and my mother\Na Priest, so I guess I'm a Warrior Priest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.50,0:08:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Avan taught me Healing and\NSupport-type spells and some martial arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.75,0:08:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't use attack spells...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.84,0:08:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So he gave you the Magic Bullet Gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.18,0:08:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. At my graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.60,0:09:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forget that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Your certificate of graduation.\NAn Insignia of Avan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.73,0:09:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, anywhere you go,\Nyou're officially a protector of justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.03,0:09:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is a present from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A present?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.62,0:09:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, what is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.33,0:09:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A Magic Bullet Gun. A great weapon\Nthat lets you charge and fire magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.80,0:09:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it based on research documents...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.49,0:09:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want this scary item!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to be like Mom and Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.29,0:09:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to protect\Neveryone in the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.78,0:09:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam, you truly are a gentle soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.40,0:09:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But Maam...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.24,0:10:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,there are times when love and kindness\Naren't enough to protect people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as strength without justice\Nis powerless,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.53,0:10:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,so too is justice without strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.59,0:10:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, not only will this weapon\Nboost your attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.80,0:10:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but it can save people\Nwith Healing and Support-type spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all in how you use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.98,0:10:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.94,0:10:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,In your hands, this will never\Nbecome power without justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I guarantee it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Avan...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.12,0:10:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a little silly,\Nbut strong and kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.54,0:10:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He truly was a wonderful teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man. I suddenly miss him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At first I thought she seemed boorish.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now that I look at her, Maam's actually...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:17.53,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,MAGIC BULLET GUN
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.99,0:11:22.53,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}IO{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\NEXPLOSION-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Pathetic! Disciple of Avan or not,\NI let that child best me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.63,0:11:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see you're in a bad mood, Crocodine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Who dares?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not that I blame you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.26,0:11:50.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not after some mere children\Nscarred you so.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Zaboera!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Good to see you, Beast King.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.38,0:12:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know of my wound?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.90,0:12:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The Heyedra, watchers of the battlefield,\Nbelong to my Mystic Legion.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing I do not know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.42,0:12:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And? Have you come to laugh at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.92,0:12:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Learning of your plight,\NI've come to offer my aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You?! Offer to aid me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.97,0:12:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,As a fellow Legion Commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I should go see the village elder.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.95,0:12:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.04,0:12:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to ask him to load\Nthese bullets with attack spells.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.69,0:12:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The elder is\Nthe best spell caster in the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll do it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.22,0:12:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations, Maam.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.72,0:12:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp hardly ever does anything for anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:12:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Back me up a little, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.67,0:13:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of that then.\NI'll go prepare dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.18,0:13:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't tell her that Master Avan died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.39,0:13:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But Master Avan really is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,So many people admire him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.03,0:13:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.82,0:13:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I should fill these up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.28,0:13:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.33,0:13:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.14,0:13:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.22,0:13:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa, whoa, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's his problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.34,0:13:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You'd have me use\Nsuch a dirty tactic?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.07,0:13:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no dirty or clean\Nin defeating an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.15,0:13:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.61,0:13:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need your dirty help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.97,0:13:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fight him fair and square and win!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.12,0:13:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.08,0:14:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy, Dai, cannot be underestimated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.32,0:14:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently he cut off Lord Hadlar's hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.82,0:14:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, if you should happen to fail
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.93,0:14:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,you won't have a seat left\Nin the Dark Army, Crocodine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Hadlar may be aware of Dai's power,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but what will the other four\NLegion Commanders say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.59,0:14:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,"So Crocodine, the Beast King,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.45,0:14:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,was a fool who\Ncouldn't even kill a child."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.02,0:14:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for your own good. Use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't want to lose\Nyour current position, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.53,0:14:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's to defeat Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.00,0:15:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a favor to ask!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.60,0:15:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Please train me in magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't be saying I'm no good at spells\Nwhen fighting the Dark Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.28,0:15:15.85,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true that I am\Nthe best Mage in the village,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm not good enough\Nto teach a student of Sir Avan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.56,0:15:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Magic training?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.48,0:15:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I was only trained by Master Avan\Nfor three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.82,0:15:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Elder, you can't let Maam\Nor her mother know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Master is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.22,0:15:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Master Avan...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,died.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.75,0:15:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.14,0:15:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He was protecting us from the Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to get stronger!\NTo avenge Master Avan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.89,0:15:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a disciple of Avan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.81,0:16:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.54,0:16:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-Okay.\N-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam's shut herself in her room.\NI wonder what's wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.86,0:16:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.07,0:16:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master Avan...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Master...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.96,0:16:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Looking good this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.73,0:16:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now cast it forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.13,0:16:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Mera!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.59,0:16:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Another failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.10,0:16:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.32,0:16:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He threw the fireball!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.60,0:16:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Well done, young Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.35,0:16:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally managed to do a spell on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.90,0:16:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What does he mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, sometimes this mark lights up\Non his forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.26,0:17:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,When it does, he gets real strong\Nand casts amazing spells,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.51,0:17:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but normally, he can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.35,0:17:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Hyado!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.00,0:17:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,He's pretty weird, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.17,0:17:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A mark on their forehead... A crest?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.89,0:17:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The ones who can use\Nany fighting skill or spell.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.39,0:17:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've heard of such a race\Nof ultimate knights, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.40,0:17:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He couldn't be.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Mera!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.03,0:17:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.19,0:17:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Talk about a forced spell.\NYou can't call that a success.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.30,0:17:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now. It just needs to hit his target.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.20,0:17:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He uses ingenuity to overcome weakness.\NHe's a clever lad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.73,0:17:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I can't get complacent!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Here goes, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You're leaving tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.03,0:17:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.18,0:18:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you were going to\NRomos Castle. What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,To help the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.53,0:18:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We heard he's being\Nthreatened by monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam seems kind of down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:15.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Dai,\Nwhy don't we tell Maam the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? We can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But she might decide to join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But Maam has her duty\Nto protect this village.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.27,0:18:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.98,0:18:29.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, you like Maam, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.42,0:18:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,W-W-What are you talking about?!\NW-Why should I like her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Liar. You're always staring at her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.07,0:18:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I am not! Forget it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.83,0:18:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Get to sleep! Goodnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye, Gomechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.20,0:19:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.80,0:19:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye Maam. Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.92,0:19:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I really wanted\Nto go with you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.30,0:19:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's okay. The elder gave us\Na map of the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.57,0:19:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye! I promise to come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.32,0:19:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll come, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,They're good boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.41,0:19:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So young, yet they're\Nstanding up to the Dark Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Maam?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They're both risking their lives\Nto avenge Master Avan, and yet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.41,0:19:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam, go on after them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to help them, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.75,0:20:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about us. Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.63,0:20:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.89,0:20:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I once left this village, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.60,0:20:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,After I saw Sir Avan and your father\Nfighting even when they were wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.67,0:20:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're my daughter. It's in your blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.44,0:20:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam, don't worry about the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.80,0:20:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have strength in me yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.59,0:20:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.60,0:20:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll protect the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.60,0:20:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Go help Gomechan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.59,0:20:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.34,0:20:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.30,0:20:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Or this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.41,0:20:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're like this even with a map?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.19,0:21:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.78,0:21:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.32,0:21:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai! Popp! I'm coming with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:06.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.91,0:21:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Good for you, Popp.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I just figured she'd be useful in a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.89,0:21:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.38,0:21:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're both disciples of Avan,\Nthen I'm your senior.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to carry on\NMaster Avan's will and fight, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Maam?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.60,0:21:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.19,0:21:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell me on the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.90,0:21:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.61,0:21:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I think she's going to be\Nbossing us around.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.74,0:21:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That means she's reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.54,0:21:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.19,0:22:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kindness is the magic of kind people{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.19,0:22:25.94,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yasashisa wa yasashii hito ga tsukaeru mahou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then do I have no choice\NBut to just be a normal person?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:32.95,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}jaa boku wa tada no hito de iru shikanaino?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.12,0:22:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.12,0:22:36.16,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doudarou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if the place I call home may change{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.46,0:22:44.13,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kaeru basho wa ne kawatte yuku kedo{\i0}
